room_title: Escape room "Wizard's Workshop" by 60out Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 13336 Beach Ave Marina Del Rey, CA 90292
room_description: You are the students of a wizard. Unfortunately, your teacher made a mistake during an experiment and became a soul without a body. You, his new students, need to put the little magic you've learned to use so you can save him before he completely disappears into the fourth dimension.
